Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.48,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Odd Jobs Gin-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:35.09,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.09,0:01:37.08,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It won't make a sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:38.49,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Gin-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:42.37,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Sugar Content
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:42.37,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The damn TV just closed its eyes \Nwith a dark look on its face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.76,0:01:44.79,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it has something on its mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:46.48,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't adjusted to \Nthe digital transition?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:48.63,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably time to buy a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.11,0:01:49.93,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:52.66,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Is this how the TV always looked?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:53.77,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.77,0:01:54.96,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:58.68,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Some guy from Edobashi Camera \Nbrought it over the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:01.97,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's from one of our clients?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:03.25,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember taking any
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.25,0:02:04.90,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,jobs that involved \Ndefective merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:05.62,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:07.38,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it turned on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:08.98,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san, the TV's fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:14.14,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone familiar on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.14,0:02:16.30,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,A face I didn't want to see \Nis sticking out of the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:19.16,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,This is a 3D TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:21.45,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, 3D? That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:23.58,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,How do I turn it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:27.05,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Press your lips against the button here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:27.83,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:30.72,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Sadaharu, turn the TV off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.72,0:02:32.08,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And turn her off while you're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:34.43,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Bulk trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:36.37,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.37,0:02:37.82,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:40.68,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:46.22,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:48.47,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:50.50,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Just that my glasses broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.59,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Were they important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:53.19,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:54.44,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:56.09,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:57.63,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:02:58.53,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,They were cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:02:59.80,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:01.72,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that they were \Nfrom my late grandmother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:02.67,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.67,0:03:03.44,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:06.31,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You should probably buy a new pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:07.28,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:08.44,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:10.21,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,They're all I have to remember \Nher by, but I'm fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:11.48,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,so don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.90,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,But you're crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:15.16,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:16.89,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that a piece \Nof lens got in my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:17.85,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:20.97,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, it looks okay, but \Nyour eyes are totally red.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:22.80,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,You should go to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:24.46,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to take you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:25.29,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:26.82,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:28.27,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Just ignore those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:29.79,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:30.48,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Sa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:32.23,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:33.95,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong with this situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:35.99,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it all awkward \Nlike I accidentally hit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:38.73,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,a girl in the face while \Nplaying dodgeball?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:40.83,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It was clearly her fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:42.49,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,She basically moved her face
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:44.62,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,into the ball and broke her glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:46.80,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Gin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:48.90,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long since
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:51.29,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,my last appearance that I overdid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:52.68,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:53.79,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be leaving then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:55.13,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Sa-chan-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:57.91,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you looking at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:03:59.10,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:01.13,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Even you, Sadaharu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:07.14,On Screen,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,Glasses Are Part of the Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:09.14,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Glasses for Edogawa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:11.02,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,They're all so lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:12.89,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Which one should I pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:14.74,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:17.59,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san buying a pair \Nof glasses for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:22.40,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Both Nearsighted and Farsighted
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:20.53,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for breaking, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:22.40,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let your death be for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:24.34,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Which should I pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:27.30,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should ask \NGin-san to pick for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:30.37,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,How about one of the pairs \Nin that clearance bin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:33.09,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:34.74,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,But if this is what you like,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:36.10,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:37.01,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Do they fit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:38.17,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,How do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:39.36,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Cute, very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:45.93,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Super Cheap
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:40.91,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You look perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:44.07,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Like you were born wearing those.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:45.93,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:49.18,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Are you searching for \Nengagement glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:50.94,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are engagement glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:51.81,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of those!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:53.34,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:55.31,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,haven't we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:59.57,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady, I see that \Nyou have excellent taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:01.82,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,There's a story behind those glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:04.58,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,The lens used in the famous \NBattle of Red Cliffs
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:07.08,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,by the Wu to set fire \Nto Cao Cao's forces
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:08.54,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,were made by a man whose glasses lenses
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:10.05,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,were made by a man whose glasses lenses
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:11.79,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,were made by a man whose glasses \Nlenses were seen by a man
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:12.91,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,who wore this particular \Npair of glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:14.83,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't mean a damn thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:16.71,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take these, Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:20.45,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Since they're used, \Ngive us a 99% discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:21.70,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:23.82,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,There's a story behind those glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:26.61,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,The lens used in the famous Trojan \NHorse during the Trojan War...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:31.16,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Thank you, Gin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:32.97,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to show
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:35.22,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,my gratitude for these \Nwonderful glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:37.76,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I've never received such a \Nwonderful and stinky present.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:39.35,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:41.98,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you walk her home, "Gin-san"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:46.10,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask Gengai to fix \Nyour Grandma's glasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.89,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,so just use those for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:49.26,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:50.00,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:54.78,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma would yell at me \Nfor clinging to the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:57.06,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:59.80,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma's glasses which \Nwere stepped on by Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:00.95,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,who was stepped on by Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:02.21,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,who stepped on the poop \Nof a dog whose owner
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:04.09,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,had a daughter that owned the \Nstore which sold these glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:04.73,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:06.59,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't mean a damn thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:10.57,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think of these glasses \Nas you and never let them go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:12.39,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treasure them forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:16.89,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:26.65,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Open wide!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:53.30,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Love Garden
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:56.31,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Put on the damn glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:58.86,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The hell are you doing \Nwith those glasses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:07:00.81,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you going on a date and going \Nall the way with a pair of glasses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:04.26,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san, are you jealous of Glassin-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:05.68,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is Glassin-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:07.13,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong, Gin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:10.44,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning on putting \Non Glassin-san right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:12.92,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,But when I thought of them as you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:14.33,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,I got all nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:17.36,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm finally ready now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:19.58,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to p-put...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:24.84,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Love Garden
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:20.73,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:21.74,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,It's too embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:23.09,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you making the act of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:24.84,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,putting on glasses sound so dirty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:26.85,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,But they're like another you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:29.44,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,If I put them on, it's like, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:31.17,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us become one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:32.56,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,How can you turn the act of putting
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.05,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,on glasses into such a big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.59,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And those are like another random
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:37.10,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,old guy who owns the glasses store.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:38.85,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.28,0:07:41.94,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I got your glasses fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:43.85,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Just throw away that filthy pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.28,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:47.15,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want your \Nglasses broken again,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:49.42,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,never sneak into our house again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:50.86,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:54.38,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,How can you come slinking back
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:56.21,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and acting like you're my boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.75,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:58.87,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:01.74,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm devoted to Glassin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:02.75,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I want Glassin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.75,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be Glassin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:07.69,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even imagine wearing \Nanother pair of glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:09.17,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat me like one of those
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:11.35,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,loose-eared sluts that \Nconstantly switches glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:12.63,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The hell is a loose-eared slut?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:16.74,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I got these fixed because \Nyou kept complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:19.09,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, those glasses \Naren't your prescription,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:20.13,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,so you can't see a thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:21.40,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:23.76,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Leave Glassin-san and me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:25.38,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,It's too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:26.89,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late to try \Nto be nice to me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:28.02,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:30.36,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it sound like a love triangle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:33.11,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Never show your face around \NGlassin-san and me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:35.06,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, former glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:36.29,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, former lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:42.29,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy you a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:44.33,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:46.14,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I feel like I was just dumped?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:48.79,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Is this country full of idiots?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:54.55,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Dango House
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:52.55,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,The target?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:54.55,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,A government official, \NZenkichiro Yoneda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:56.42,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Preparations have been made by
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:57.76,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,previously dispatched agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:08:59.18,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Your mission is to rendezvous
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:00.81,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,with the agents and take out the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:03.75,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Will you return to the path of evil
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:06.81,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,for the sake of saving \Nthe weak masses, Sa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:11.32,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, evil can only \Nbe eradicated by evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:17.58,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm willing to get my hands \Nbloody to save others...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:19.38,Main01,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Sa-chan, those aren't dango.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:24.47,Main01,Yoneda,0000,0000,0000,,Echimoya, you're so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:27.58,Main01,Echimoya,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I pale in comparison to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:28.84,Main01,Yoneda,0000,0000,0000,,Come closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:32.63,Main01,Yoneda,0000,0000,0000,,I have a question to ask \Nyou before we begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.97,Main01,Yoneda,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:37.59,Main01,Echimoya,0000,0000,0000,,Intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:41.18,Main01,Men,0000,0000,0000,,Damn intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:42.68,Main01,Men,0000,0000,0000,,Cut 'em all down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:44.31,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll act as a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:48.62,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,While I draw their attention, \Nyou all should escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:50.20,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,But Sa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:51.23,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:55.18,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't unleash my \Nstrength with you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.18,0:09:56.43,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Sa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:09:58.61,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Now hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:00.24,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:03.57,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Sarutobi, I'll make this easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.57,0:10:04.62,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Switch glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.86,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you're not getting \Nany assassination work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:09.50,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Only makes sense after all the mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:12.13,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and you even injured your own men.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:16.78,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,There are rumors that you're in a slump,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:18.54,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,but you can't fool me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:21.39,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see a thing, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:23.50,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:26.89,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see what I'm doing right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:28.42,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:29.90,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:30.93,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:34.69,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm applying Preparation \NH in front of your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:38.49,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:40.01,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,You're using your mastery of your other
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:41.67,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,senses to compensate for \Nthe lack of eyesight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:44.66,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,However, a ninja lives \Nand dies by the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:47.46,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to become a member of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:49.04,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the Oniwaban despite your poor eyesight
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:51.89,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,because of natural talent and hard work,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:55.05,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,but those custom-made Iga \Nglasses also played a role...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:57.36,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you wearing those glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.58,0:11:00.93,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,You should know very well that \Nthis world isn't a playground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:07.67,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.07,0:11:10.31,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,If I decide to wear these glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:13.06,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't find any work...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:16.04,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,If only it were that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:18.94,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,The way things stand, you're \Ngonna get yourself killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:23.75,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,The former head assassins \Nare acting suspiciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:29.46,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Does Sarutobi intend to desert?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:32.10,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,She may intend to defect \Nto a different group
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:35.46,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and provide them with information on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:36.87,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she doesn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:38.27,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,she could still create headaches
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:42.41,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,by getting herself captured \Nand leaking information.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:46.51,Main01,D,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to take her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:53.34,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've lost their trust, \Nthey'll come for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:57.23,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,The Assassins of Assassins Squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:12:00.24,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,The Lethal Punishers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.05,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,P-Punishment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:06.25,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Does it involve whips and candles \Nand things of that nature?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:08.24,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:12.93,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,These assassins are trained \Nto kill assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:15.79,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Do you stand a chance \Nwith those glasses on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:19.51,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what happens to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:22.58,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,but if you die a dog's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:26.00,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,it'll make the rest of the \Nformer Oniwabanshu look bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:28.98,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Try to avoid that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.11,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,These were the first...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:37.02,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,The first present from Gin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:41.03,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not allowed to wear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:06.89,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that you are \NLady Ayame Sarutobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:08.49,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:15.01,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I see that nobody ever \Ntaught you any manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:17.18,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,A gentleman would
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:20.40,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,never interrupt a girl who's crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:22.55,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,My policy is to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:26.41,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,gently wipe away the \Ntears when a woman cries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:28.28,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:29.91,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,How kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:32.41,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:34.37,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,...when the woman happens to be \Nyour target for assassination?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:45.92,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wipe away your tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:49.80,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll wipe away your blood, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.56,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Ayame Sarutobi the assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:57.18,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,Our superiors have \Ndetermined that you are
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:58.65,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,no longer necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:01.29,Main01,All,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, we Lethal Punishers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:03.94,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,have been charged with your disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:12.45,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,If you have any last words, \Nwe'll hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:14.40,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have anything to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:18.83,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:23.56,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,Would you let me put on my glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:29.47,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Greater Edo Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:30.77,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:33.47,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to die a dog's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:36.73,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why did this happen to Sa-chan-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:38.73,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Look at these.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:40.83,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,She kept wearing these glasses
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:42.79,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,when they weren't the \Nright prescription.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:45.02,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, she kept \Nscrewing up on the job
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:46.99,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and attracted the attention \Nof the higher-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:50.42,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,When I found her on the verge of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:53.49,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,she was still holding those glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:56.95,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care how happy they made her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:58.75,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,She's a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:02.75,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Can you dispose of those?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:05.13,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Greater Edo Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.13,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,They'll find this place very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:08.63,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,She won't stand a chance \Nif those are still around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:12.14,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if she still \Nrefuses to put these on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:15.51,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,that's the end of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:17.21,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hemorrhoid ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:20.52,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to leave \NSa-chan all alone here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:26.07,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but ninja don't band \Ntogether the way samurai do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:30.03,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to \Ndie, stay away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:33.16,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that's what she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:36.85,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:41.29,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:45.79,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,They were a present from Gin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:50.56,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I promised to treasure them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:16:01.60,Main01,Sa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I broke my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.43,0:16:05.78,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Sa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.46,0:16:15.62,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to see a thing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:18.47,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't need to see a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:21.54,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,When you wake up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:23.62,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,there won't be any \Ncracks in your vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:25.38,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:27.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:29.21,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who broke her glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:35.27,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The Assassins of Assassins \Nof Assassins Squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:37.43,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Lethal Odd Jobs is moving out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:26.19,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,The hell are you doing in my house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:28.35,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you sneaking \Ninto my house in the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:30.39,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,middle of night to make fried \Nrice all dramatic-like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:32.15,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,And turn off the damn music!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:33.52,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,It's bothering the neighbors!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:35.72,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:37.82,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:40.90,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, people usually get \Nhungry around this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:42.20,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So we were making a little snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:44.09,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up. This is my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:45.99,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Those are my eggs, my ham.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:47.21,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,My fried rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:48.63,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:50.81,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,We made enough for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:52.21,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the issue here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:54.32,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking why you're in my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:55.44,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you actually \Ncame here to make fried ri--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:57.51,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sadaharu's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:17:58.20,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:17:59.75,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Just set her down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:01.11,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, wait. Er, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:02.55,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bring Sarutobi here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:05.51,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're going to \Ntake on the assassins,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:07.73,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,but we don't want to \Nfight in a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:10.26,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,So we were trying to find a good place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:11.86,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:13.39,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rich and own a big house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:14.70,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Plus I'm single so \Nnobody else is around,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:16.21,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,so nobody else will be inconvenienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:17.32,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,That's the logic you used.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:18.64,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of logic is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:19.43,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:20.66,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We're just borrowing your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:21.64,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:23.57,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We're just gonna kill \Nfour or five assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.57,0:18:25.75,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to turn my \Nhouse into a murder scene?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:27.59,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you eating?!\NGet out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:30.15,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want blood and \Ninnards all over my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:32.25,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually a clean freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:36.05,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're still single.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:38.63,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Women can't stand men who are perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:42.13,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,The ideal would be a man \Nwhose room is a little messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:44.14,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That's way too big of a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:45.64,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Gin-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:48.35,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the trap is \Nset, where do we wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:49.02,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:50.15,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Seriously, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:52.29,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,How about the ceiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:52.97,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:53.97,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm seriously gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:55.90,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll assassinate your ass \Nbefore the assassins get here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:57.80,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:58.82,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:00.12,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I got it so stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:00.97,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:01.92,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:04.29,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,So stop destroying my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:13.90,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:14.92,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.34,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right above Sarutobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:19.03,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Is everybody in position?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:20.96,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. Everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:23.10,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,It's really hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:25.85,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:29.07,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,It's not perfect, but \NI did what I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.07,0:19:30.60,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,We're up against professional killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:33.03,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,They know that Sarutobi and \Nthe rest of you are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.03,0:19:35.02,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be extremely cautious,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:38.11,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,so we can use that to our advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:39.86,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura  Shinpachi  Sadaharu  \NSarutobi  Zenzo  Gintoki
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:41.85,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I left the entrance to the room where \NSarutobi is completely unguarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:45.24,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Enemy  Enemy  Enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:43.75,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,So they won't come from that direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:45.78,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,It's clearly a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:47.87,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,They'll circle around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:50.65,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,If anything goes wrong, \Nlet us know immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:54.38,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Be ready to react if they \Ncome through the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:55.83,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.83,0:19:58.13,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,And don't destroy my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:19:58.88,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:19:59.87,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:01.75,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:07.39,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, why do I have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:08.39,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:09.16,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:10.74,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Was someone asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:12.14,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Someone sounded asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:14.38,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calling roll again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:15.02,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:21.89,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:23.46,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:25.28,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody ran off to Don Quijote!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.41,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:28.04,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to help here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:30.86,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Get your ass back here, \Nwhoever went to Don Quijote!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:32.01,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:34.40,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shinpachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:36.75,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Help me put Kagura on Sadaharu's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:39.07,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,You all went to Don Quijote!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:39.90,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:42.80,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,One of you is asleep in Don Quijote?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:45.13,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,The hell is going on?!\NWhy did they all ditch me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:47.30,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,They could have invited me along!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:48.55,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I wanted to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:49.64,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:52.11,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Could you buy some Preparation H?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:54.48,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out. The suppository type.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:57.92,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:20:59.25,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:03.63,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Stop lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:05.48,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pretend to be asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:08.08,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Even the dog was \Npretending to be asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:10.18,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,The bastards are toying with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:11.13,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:11.90,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Screw this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:13.83,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:15.24,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,This sensation...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.74,0:21:17.28,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:20.13,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Two on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:22.23,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,One inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:24.94,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,And in the yard...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:31.09,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,I can smell multiple humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:33.18,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,As expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:36.99,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't matter \Nhow many there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.99,0:21:39.36,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,This time, we'll finish her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:41.86,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Along with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:44.49,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.25,0:21:47.74,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, do you have \Nany Preparation H?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.03,0:21:50.24,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,The hell are they doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.67,0:21:55.50,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.99,0:21:58.88,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry back!
