Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:32.19,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.19,0:23:34.97,Main01,Zenzo,0000,0000,0000,,Glasses prevent you from \Nseeing certain things.
